{"body": "Obviously it is your call, but I did poll several people off-line (including a former English teacher), and also posted the query below.  To date, 100% of people I have talked to believe your current usage runs counter to the true sense of the word, even if you could argue it is technically grammatical. \r\n\r\nhttp://english.stackexchange.com/questions/129909/usage-of-prohibited-vs-prevented-in-a-given-sentence\r\n\r\nPS It's probably in every Rails book because it is in the Rails software, not because it is correct :-)\r\n\r\n", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/25691573", "created_at": "2013-10-04T11:10:50Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/12434#issuecomment-25691573", "updated_at": "2013-10-04T11:10:50Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 12434, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/eykamp", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/0adf5ccd7069c2432e34bebc153ceed6?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F43a80abb431ff5e26c7e09d98eb045fa.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0adf5ccd7069c2432e34bebc153ceed6", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "eykamp", "type": "User", "id": 1133323, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/eykamp/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "52503715bd35437be6002086"}, "id": 25691573, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/12434"}
